The current system of governance upholds much of idealistic and innovative policies that will propel Africa to the political world stage. Leaders have indulged in 2022 politics yet voters have not felt much development. Initially, the presidential seat takes time to negotiate on. How electoral offices handle presidential elections does not reflect the will of voters. Kenyans believe we have a political dynasty which will not change. Reconstructing the election body to be independent will lead to fair elections and removing that belief.  Emuhaya